  "slug": "loaf-cats",
  "title": "Loaf Cats",
  "description": "Add cute little 'loaf' cats to your Minecraft world! Each cat spawns in a different biome. Once tamed, loaf mode can be activated. The magical healing powers of the cat will be released when they purr.",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/944/758/loafcats_banner_crop.png\" /></p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\">A lightweight mod which adds cute <strong style=\"color: #ff00ff;\">Loaf Cats</strong> to your world ^-^</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 18px; color: #ff0000;\"><strong>!</strong> This mod is dependent on <a style=\"color: #ff0000;\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/geckolib\">GeckoLib for Forge 1.20.1</a>. Please ensure you have this mod before running the game.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Video Showcase</strong></span></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Check out this <span style=\"color: #f583da;\">video showcase of LoafCats</span>, made by me.</span></p>\n<iframe style=\"display: table; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/hQ0ZJ3bXHs0?si=I42mKfduuGtPZrCJ\" width=\"400\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>New Update Alert!!</strong></span></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #f583da;\">There is a <strong>new update</strong> for LoafCats! Check out the features in this video:</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #f583da;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/_cM2MfbNG6U\" width=\"560\" height=\"314\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></span></span></p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Types of Loaf Cat</strong></h2>\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\">There are <strong>12</strong> different types for you to find - each spawns in a different biome.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/944/798/catvariants.png\" width=\"807\" height=\"454\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">In recent updates, new Loaf Cats have been added! The most recent additions are highlighted :D</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1086899/description_1dc187e5-9293-418b-8751-f5b5c3da2253.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"259\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1086899/description_b523805e-2eee-459e-9af7-5f0f17f2c9f0.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"259\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1086899/description_53061ea0-d629-4c4a-8408-dae876f2d397.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"243\"></span></p>  \n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Loaf Mode</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\">Once you have tamed a Loaf Cat, you can put it into <strong style=\"color: #ff00ff;\">Loaf Mode</strong> by right-clicking on it. The cat will then sit down in a loaf position and relax.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\">You can make your cat happy and affectionate by staying close to it while it is in Loaf Mode. Once it is happy enough, it will purr, and you will experience the healing effects.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/944/820/2024-08-19_13.png\" width=\"786\" height=\"442\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Additionally, the Loaf Cat will cuddle with you and enter Loaf Mode when you sleep in a bed.</span></p>\n\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Living with the Loaf Cats</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\">To <strong style=\"color: #ff00ff;\">tame</strong> a Loaf Cat, use a Cat Treat.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\">If your cat ever gets <strong style=\"color: #ff0000;\">damaged</strong>, you can <strong style=\"color: #99cc00;\">heal</strong> it by feeding it Cat Food. Be careful not to attack a Loaf Cat—if it doesn't trust you, it will fight back!</p>\n\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Crafting Recipes</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/944/819/recipes.png\" width=\"803\" height=\"452\" /></p>\n\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Loafcat Breeding</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\">To breed two Loaf Cats, feed them both <strong style=\"color: #cc99ff;\">Catnip</strong>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/944/821/2024-08-19_13.png\" width=\"791\" height=\"445\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\">Catnip is a flower which can be found only in Plains, Forest, and Flower Forest biomes.</p>\n\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Audio</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\">All sound effects in this mod are taken from recordings of my cat, Bean.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/6Dk82tr/meandbean.png\" width=\"345\" height=\"194\" /></p>\n\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Thank you ^-^</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\">Thank you for taking the time to view my mod. I hope you enjoy!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\">Comments are always appreciated to help me improve my work.</p>\n",
